## Optional: Sentry Integration

This worker includes optional Sentry error tracking. To enable:

1. Add your Sentry DSN to `wrangler.jsonc`:
   ```jsonc
   "vars": {
     "SENTRY_DSN": "https://your-sentry-dsn@sentry.io/your-project-id"
   }
   ```

2. Optionally add the `withSentry` middleware for request tracing:
   ```typescript
   import { withSentry } from '@repo/hono-helpers'

   app.use('*', withSentry({ op: 'http.server' }))
   ```

For more advanced usage (instrumenting handlers, Durable Objects, or Workflows), see the `@repo/hono-helpers` package documentation.
